name: Loek Kasiib, The Abyss
text:
Reach, annihilator 3

When Loek Kasiib, The Abyss enters the battlefield, gain control of all flooded lands until Loek Kasiib leaves the battlefield. 

When Loek Kasiib, The Abyss is put into a graveyard from anywhere, its owner shuffles their graveyard into their library.
